org.gephi.lib.gleem.linalg

Class Matf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gephi.lib.gleem.linalg.Matf

  • public class Matf
extends Object
    Arbitrary-size single-precision matrix class. Currently very simple and only supports a few needed operations.
